text: If anyone has any experience with HubSpot calls, transcriptions, etc, please DM me! I just have a few questions.

Now we are stuck, since our developer is saying that he cannot increase the speed anymore due to limitations of HubSpot. Anyone know of any examples of a 90+ Pagespeed score with HubSpot CMS and can give us some feedback?
